---
title: Mobile-tour
---
extends layouts/_layout
block content
  .mobile_tour
    section.mobile_tour__intro
      .container
        .row.middle-xs
          .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.last-xs
            .mobile_tour__intro__img.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
              img(src="img/mobile_tour/pwa.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/pwa@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/pwa@3x.png 3x")
          .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.last-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1s")
            h1 Digital Kit
            p A revolutionary new concept of delivering post purchase experience and engaging with customers through a single powerful mobile interface.
            p (Accessible over App, Mobile Web & PWA)
            a(href="#")
              img(src="img/icon/play-icon.png" srcset="img/icon/play-icon@2x.png 2x, img/icon/play-icon@3x.png 3x")
              | Watch Video
    section.mobile_tour__experience
      .container
        h2 Digital Kits help you re-invent your consumer relationships
        p Give digital consumers an amazing digital experience
        .mobile_tour__experience__content
          .mobile_tour__experience__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
            .mobile_tour__experience__block__img
              img(src="img/mobile_tour/ce-01.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/ce-01@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/ce-01@3x.png 3x")
            .mobile_tour__experience__block__text
              strong Give a complete makeover to post purchase convenience
              p Provide the entire post purchase experience with an easy to use mobile channel, enable super simple interactions, automate repetitive activities with user permissions and offer smart recommendation to help customers get an enriching and fulflling product experience.
          .mobile_tour__experience__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
            .mobile_tour__experience__block__img
              img(src="img/mobile_tour/ce-04.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/ce-04@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/ce-04@3x.png 3x")
            .mobile_tour__experience__block__text
              strong With the NHANCE NOW mobile channels you can " with "With Digital Kits you can
              p Customers usually feel a sense of abandonement after the purchase phase. With the NHANCE NOW mobile channels you can now “live” the entire post purchase journey with them, digitally handholding them through important stages.
          .mobile_tour__experience__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
            .mobile_tour__experience__block__img
              img(src="img/mobile_tour/ce-03.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/ce-03@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/ce-03@3x.png 3x")
            .mobile_tour__experience__block__text
              strong Offer a full spectrum of brand experiences to amplify brand value
              p Provide a full range of brand services in a completely new format. Empower customers with on-demand access to important product information, delight them with hyper personalized interactions and proactively engage with them to transmit a better ownership experience.
    section.mobile_tour__capability
      .container
        .mobile_tour__capability__title
          h2 Digital Kits Empower Customers
          p Transfer control of post purchase customer experience into the hands of your consumers
        .mobile_tour__capability__block
          .row.middle-xs.center-xs
            .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.end-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
              h3 One Stop Mobile Hub
              p Provide all post purchase engagement on a single mobile experience platform. Help customers discover special offers, access all brand services, make purchases, and stay in touch with you at all times.
              p Its customer experience like never before and helps your customers easily manage product or service journeys.
            .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.start-sm
              .mobile_tour__capability__block__img.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
                img(src="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-01.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-01@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/key-feature-01@3x.png 3x")
        .mobile_tour__capability__block
          .row.middle-xs.center-xs
            .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.end-sm.last-xs
              .mobile_tour__capability__block__img.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
                img(src="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-02.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-02@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/key-feature-02@3x.png 3x")
            .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.start-sm.last-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
              h3 Help Center
              p Provide resolutions to queries instantly. Lets customers choose from a list of curated resolutions to most common queries or raise service requests for specific issues.
              p Help center are the ideal alternative support channels which offer a quick first line of support enabling fast, fulfilling on-demand customer support.
        .mobile_tour__capability__block
          .row.middle-xs.center-xs
            .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.end-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
              h3 Do It Yourself
              p Provide a range of self help resources in easy to consume videos, images and document files. You customers get an on-demand knowledgebase and training artefacts to quicken product adopton and improve product usage.
              p Its every customers’ digital assistant, available 24x7 to help them get the best value out of every product or service.
            .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.start-sm
              .mobile_tour__capability__block__img.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
                img(src="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-03.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-03@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/key-feature-03@3x.png 3x")
        .mobile_tour__capability__block
          .row.middle-xs.center-xs
            .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.end-sm.last-xs
              .mobile_tour__capability__block__img.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
                img(src="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-04.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-04@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/key-feature-04@3x.png 3x")
            .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.start-sm.last-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
              h3 Personalized Interactions
              p Send intelligent and contextual recommendations that are meant just for your customers! No more irrelevant messages that spam. Every interaction is mapped to the product or service that your customers own..	
        .mobile_tour__capability__block
          .row.middle-xs.center-xs
            .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.end-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
              h3 Digital Documents
              p Move away from cumbersome paper products and provide invoices, warranties, safety manuals,intstruction guides in digital lossless formats. You can even let your customers add invoices to access purchase details.
              p Digitization is the best way of eliminiating fake documents and allows anytime, anywhere access of documents and peace of mind for your customers.
            .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.start-sm
              .mobile_tour__capability__block__img.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
                img(src="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-05.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-05@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/key-feature-05@3x.png 3x")
        .mobile_tour__capability__block
          .row.middle-xs.center-xs
            .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.end-sm.last-xs
              .mobile_tour__capability__block__img.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
                img(src="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-06.png" srcset="img/mobile_tour/key-feature-06@2x.png 2x, img/mobile_tour/key-feature-06@3x.png 3x")
            .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.start-sm.last-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1.5s")
              h3 Complimentary Purchases
              p Enable quick discovery and 1-tap purchase of key complimentary services like extended warranty, insurances and various other add-ons with a simple intuitive interface.
              p Boost your upsell and cross sell and save time for your customers by making it easy to make essential purchases right from their mobile phones.
    section.mobile_tour__advantages
      .container
        .mobile_tour__advantages__title
          h2 Few more benefits
          p There is a lot more that a digtial kit has to offer
        .row
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .mobile_tour__advantages__block.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__img
                img(src="img/icon/easy-stepup.png" srcset="img/icon/easy-stepup@2x.png 2x, img/icon/easy-stepup@3x.png 3x")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__text
                strong Product Registration
                p Enable Registration of any product in 3 easy steps.
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .mobile_tour__advantages__block.mobile_tour__advantages__block--mobile.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__img
                img(src="img/icon/pay-per-use.png" srcset="img/icon/pay-per-use@2x.png 2x, img/icon/pay-per-use@3x.png 3x")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__text
                strong Feedback
                p Collect instant feedback on any product, service or brand experience.
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .mobile_tour__advantages__block.mobile_tour__advantages__block--right.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__img
                img(src="img/icon/highly-secure.png" srcset="img/icon/highly-secure@2x.png 2x, img/icon/highly-secure@3x.png 3x")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__text
                strong View Events
                p Show all upcoming and scheduled events in one place.
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .mobile_tour__advantages__block.mobile_tour__advantages__block--border.mobile_tour__advantages__block--mobile.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__img
                img(src="img/icon/help-support.png" srcset="img/icon/help-support@2x.png 2x, img/icon/help-support@3x.png 3x")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__text
                strong Actionable Notifications
                p Include Call to Actions within all notifications.
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .mobile_tour__advantages__block.mobile_tour__advantages__block--border.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__img
                img(src="img/icon/personalized.png" srcset="img/icon/personalized@2x.png 2x, img/icon/personalized@3x.png 3x")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__text
                strong Automated Alerts
                p Send automated reminders and never let customers miss out on any important activity.
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .mobile_tour__advantages__block.mobile_tour__advantages__block--border.mobile_tour__advantages__block--right.mobile_tour__advantages__block--right-1.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__img
                img(src="img/icon/intuitive.png" srcset="img/icon/intuitive@2x.png 2x, img/icon/intuitive@3x.png 3x")
              .mobile_tour__advantages__block__text
                strong Reccommendations
                p Provide step by step reccommendations through the entire customer journey.
    section.mobile_tour__relations
      .container
        .row.center-xs
          .col-md-8.col-xs-12
            h2 Show your consumers how much you care about their experience
            p Connect with one of our product specialists to understand <br>how your business can benefit from NHANCE NOW
            a(href="#").btn.btn-primary Schedule a demo